snippet.title: CLEANING THE WORLD WITH PAMPAM - Game Jam Version! Dev log 3
snippet.description:
“Cleaning the Forest” - This is the first version of the game, it was created during the Fabrica de Jogos 2021 Game Jam, a game jam of 2 days. After the game jam’s live, a lot of people praised Pampam’s charisma and some people said that recycling games are usually boring and it would be cool if we continue developing the game, so here we are!
You can play it on this link: https://rerezin-das-galaxias.itch.io/cleaning-the-forest
